{
  "doc_id": "43809",
  "text": "The later sections of this paper presents a biometric cryptosystem construct called \"fuzzy vault\" which is based on iris and which was originally proposed by Juels and Sudan [CITATION_1] in \"A fuzzy vault scheme,\" in 2002 for fingerprints. This paper aims to show how biometric cryptosystem is used for providing authentication and in turn security to cryptographic keys.",
